        <meta property="og:description" content="We are Lucas (left) and João (right).


 We are both from the city of Belo Horizonte (Brazil). That’s where we met while we were studying Computer Science. During that time, we took part on game jams and did small projects. There was a point when we decided game jamming around wasn’t enough, thus in June, 2014, Long Hat House was born.


 The universe of video games is infinite and vast, it includes much of what we love in life: tech, programming, arts, music, narratives, game design &nbsp;and some more obscure subjects like psychology, sociology and other crazy stuff we often like to babble about. It is an universe we want to explore, express and create. Meet all these insane people who work on games too.


 We are mainly programmers, but we do a little bit of everything and also, sometimes receive help from friends who appreciate our work.


 Questions, critiques and hatemails go to contact@longhathouse.com. See you around and play our games!">
      

      

      

      

      

      

      

      

      

    

  

  

